{"tid":521471,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"【Orage台】三人成行，仲差一人 Day165 6/1【MHP2G】","createTime":"2018-01-06T14:53:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-06T17:37:31.000Z","uid":122942,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"10cdffed823449a0be0d9dc09fb5643be39ded78","tid":521471,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T14:53:06.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/5ADqP2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2F5ADqP2.gif&h=8c5a58f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家好，我係Orage。 我會於每晚11點至2點開台玩遊戲同與觀眾聊天。<br />\n因為我極度3分鐘熱度，所以好少會一直玩同一隻Game。<br />\n有興趣嘅巴打入黎捧下場，一齊傾下計啦  <br />\n<br />\n今晚11點左右見 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Foragejan%20&d=p%2BsVDQEEkqe1gYArcpEg2XIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=5081c3bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan </a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/W4CK8P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FW4CK8P.png&h=69cccb5f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n另外我開左個FB專頁，有時會PO日常野同覺得有趣嘅事，<br />\n希望巴打們可以入黎比個讚。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oragejan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foragejan&d=p%2BsVDQEEkqe1gYArcpEg2XIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=eb1aa94a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oragejan</a></div>"},{"pid":"a25384ec65a29258672fb66b35cea36c59ba762b","tid":521471,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T14:56:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f50d458419988419078db1c86943142e9136b57e","tid":521471,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T14:56:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d55766c8d5e8a0b98a0ff9dcbec0a57a17dbdad6","tid":521471